OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy start with
OL,6,Fshowers, perhaps some more persistent
OL,7,Frain at first in far west. Becoming
OL,8,Fbrighter with some long sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping, towards midday, the
OL,10,Fshowers becoming lighter and less
OL,11,Ffrequent. Fresh northerly winds,
OL,12,Fstrong in coastal parts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSome good spells of evening
OL,15,Fsunshine, and long clear spells
OL,16,Fovernight, with just a few showers
OL,17,Faround. Touch of frost possible in
OL,18,Fsheltered spots. Winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
