OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSunny spells and with a few
OL,6,Fshowers around through the morning,
OL,7,Fbut the afternoon looks largely dry
OL,8,Fwith more in the way of sunshine.
OL,9,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,10,Fease.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,13,Fmorning with sunny spells Saturday but
OL,14,Fcloud increasing with rain spreading
OL,15,Feast in afternoon. Sunny spells and
OL,16,Foccasionally heavy showers Sunday then
OL,17,Fmostly cloudy with rain at times
OL,18,FMonday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
